## IThreeWayDiff.identical property

True if the objects are identical, false otherwise.

When `true`<!-- -->, both `onlyInA` and `onlyInB` will be `null`<!-- -->, and `unchanged` will contain the complete shared structure. The metadata will show zero added, removed, and modified properties.

**Signature:**

```typescript
identical: boolean;
```
